(9, 'Lesson Sejarah IoT', '<div>\r\n<div data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQo_EKegQIJRAB\" data-hveid=\"CCUQAQ\"><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137163388\">Sejarah IoT </span>dimulai pada awal perkembangan teknologi komputer dan jaringan, dengan konsep modern IoT mulai berkembang pada tahun 1980-an<span data-huuid=\"4326525961137163388\"> .&nbsp;</span><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137164215\">Istilah \"Internet of Things\" pertama kali diperkenalkan oleh Kevin Ashton pada tahun 1999. Konsep IoT sebelumnya dikenal sebagai \"embedded internet\" atau \"pervasive computing\".<span data-cid=\"9f9b93fa-e1cc-4d6f-9a81-d7d26eb6cd84\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n<div data-uuids=\"4326525961137163388,4326525961137164215\" data-cid=\"9f9b93fa-e1cc-4d6f-9a81-d7d26eb6cd84\">\r\n<div tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQ3fYKegQIKRAB\" data-hveid=\"CCkQAQ\" aria-label=\"Lihat link terkait\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQo_EKegQIFBAB\" data-hveid=\"CBQQAQ\"><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137161773\">Perkembangan Key Point:</span></div>\r\n<div data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQo_EKegQIFBAB\" data-hveid=\"CBQQAQ\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQo_EKegQIFBAB\" data-hveid=\"CBQQAQ\">\r\n<p><strong>1980-an</strong>:<br>Konsep penambahan sensor dan kecerdasan pada objek fisik mulai dibahas, seperti modifikasi mesin penjual otomatis Coca-Cola untuk melacak isinya.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQm_YKegQIIhAB\" data-hveid=\"CCIQAQ\">\r\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__46\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137162639\"><strong>1999:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137163466\">Kevin Ashton, seorang ilmuwan komputer, memperkenalkan istilah \"Internet of Things\" saat bekerja di Procter &amp; Gamble, dengan fokus pada penggunaan RFID (Radio-Frequency Identification) untuk melacak produk dalam rantai pasokan.<span data-cid=\"00a70fd7-3cd7-4a6b-ac5d-a2f477087a49\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n<div data-uuids=\"4326525961137162639,4326525961137163466\" data-cid=\"00a70fd7-3cd7-4a6b-ac5d-a2f477087a49\">\r\n<div tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQ3fYKegQIeBAB\" data-hveid=\"CHgQAQ\" aria-label=\"Lihat link terkait\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__56\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137161024\"><strong>2000-an:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137161851\">LG memperkenalkan kulkas pintar pertama, dan semakin banyak perangkat terhubung yang muncul di pasaran.<span data-cid=\"c6f6bbc2-62ba-44e8-9cf3-fd40f41c1cd7\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n<div data-uuids=\"4326525961137161024,4326525961137161851\" data-cid=\"c6f6bbc2-62ba-44e8-9cf3-fd40f41c1cd7\">\r\n<div tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQ3fYKegQIeRAB\" data-hveid=\"CHkQAQ\" aria-label=\"Lihat link terkait\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__67\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137163505\"><strong>2010-an:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137160236\">Konsep ekosistem IoT mulai berkembang, dan pemerintah China menjadikan IoT sebagai prioritas strategis.<span data-cid=\"7257ec87-b279-4701-b782-2bd1d5243e5b\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n<div data-uuids=\"4326525961137163505,4326525961137160236\" data-cid=\"7257ec87-b279-4701-b782-2bd1d5243e5b\">\r\n<div tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQ3fYKegQIdxAB\" data-hveid=\"CHcQAQ\" aria-label=\"Lihat link terkait\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__34\">\r\n<div data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQo_EKegQIahAB\" data-hveid=\"CGoQAQ\"><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137161890\">Contoh Penerapan IoT:</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__30\">\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__35\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137160275\"><strong>Transportasi:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137161102\">Manajemen transportasi publik yang menggunakan sensor pada bus dan halte untuk mengirim data real-time tentang jumlah penumpang dan lokasi kendaraan.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__45\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137162756\"><strong>Kesehatan:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137163583\">Pemantauan kondisi pasien secara langsung melalui perangkat yang terhubung, dan penggunaan kecerdasan buatan (AI) serta robot perawat.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__54\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137161141\"><strong>Industri:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137161968\">Penggunaan sensor dan perangkat terhubung untuk memantau dan mengontrol proses produksi.<span data-cid=\"0b4ce36e-053f-42e8-a5d2-322d2bfb5a2a\">&nbsp;</span></span>\r\n<div data-uuids=\"4326525961137160275,4326525961137161102,4326525961137162756,4326525961137163583,4326525961137161141,4326525961137161968\" data-cid=\"0b4ce36e-053f-42e8-a5d2-322d2bfb5a2a\">\r\n<div tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQ3fYKegUIjQEQAQ\" data-hveid=\"CI0BEAE\" aria-label=\"Lihat link terkait\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__64\">\r\n<div data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJjtCI0syNAxX8yzgGHZ2CDDwQo_EKegQIaxAB\" data-hveid=\"CGsQAQ\"><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137163622\">Faktor Pendorong Perkembangan IoT:</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__31\">\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__36\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137162007\"><strong>Kemajuan teknologi sensor dan jaringan:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137162834\">Peningkatan kemampuan sensor untuk mengumpulkan data dan jaringan untuk mengirimkannya.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__47\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137160392\"><strong>Pergeseran paradigma dalam bisnis:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137161219\">Perusahaan mulai menyadari potensi IoT untuk meningkatkan efisiensi dan menjangkau pelanggan melalui perangkat terhubung.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"qmY6aMmRMvyX4-EPnYWy4AM__57\">\r\n<div data-il=\"\">\r\n<div data-crb-p=\"\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137162873\"><strong>Pergeseran paradigma dalam kehidupan sehari-hari:</strong></span></div>\r\n<div><span data-huuid=\"4326525961137163700\">Penggunaan perangkat pintar dan terhubung dalam kehidupan sehari-hari terus meningkat.<span data-cid=\"c995528f-c793-4b19-94a7-7c696194a55b\">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2025-05-27 11:10:25', 74, '2025-05-31 02:19:38');

